front.title: •A Real Hero
front.gametext: USED: Take Lobot into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  LOST: If your Lando is in a battle at a Cloud City site, add two battle destiny. OR If Han and your Lando are involved in the same battle, cancel one opponent's battle destiny just after it is revealed.

combo: Lando + A Real Hero (Lost) Two battle destinies.
Lando + any other character + A Real Hero (Lost) Three battle destinies.
Lando + A Real Hero (Used) Dark Side Lando cannot be replaced.
Lando + Darth Vader + Luke + A Real Hero +I Have You Now Five battle destinies with +1 to each.
